      "seed": 2066141298,
      "version": 323,
      "versionNonce": 1215805678,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782701641287,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Data storage\n2. Message Data structure\n3. Btching\n4. Producer flow\n5. Consumer flow\n6. Consumer rebalancing\n7. State storage\n8. Metadata storage\n9. Zookeeper\n10. Replication ( ISR)\n11. Scalability\n    Producer\n    Consumer\n    Broker\n    Partition\n12. Delivery semantics\n13. Message filtering\n14. Delayed and scheduled messages",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Data storage\n2. Message Data structure\n3. Btching\n4. Producer flow\n5. Consumer flow\n6. Consumer rebalancing\n7. State storage\n8. Metadata storage\n9. Zookeeper\n10. Replication ( ISR)\n11. Scalability\n    Producer\n    Consumer\n    Broker\n    Partition\n12. Delivery semantics\n13. Message filtering\n14. Delayed and scheduled messages",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
