    {
      "id": "cc4mR5iwIzy6_Cs40Bwi_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6635.744252163724,
      "y": 1256.8440452725624,
      "width": 1003.7391967773438,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffffff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bN2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 893220526,
      "version": 646,
      "versionNonce": 1342815278,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782701641288,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "11. Scalability\n- Producer\nProducers can be added/ removed easily\n\n- Consumer\nCOnsumers can be added/ removed, consumer to partition rebalnce is needed\n\n- Broker\nIf broker is added, distribution plan is needed, rebalncing of partion might be needed\nbroker controller detects some broker is added/ removed and generates new partition distribution plan\naccording to replication factor\nuse consisetent hashing\n\n-Partition\npartition changes for operational reasons like scaling topic, throughput tuning etc\nnumber of partition changes then partition to consumer must be rebalanced\nand producers must be informed\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "11. Scalability\n- Producer\nProducers can be added/ removed easily\n\n- Consumer\nCOnsumers can be added/ removed, consumer to partition rebalnce is needed\n\n- Broker\nIf broker is added, distribution plan is needed, rebalncing of partion might be needed\nbroker controller detects some broker is added/ removed and generates new partition distribution plan\naccording to replication factor\nuse consisetent hashing\n\n-Partition\npartition changes for operational reasons like scaling topic, throughput tuning etc\nnumber of partition changes then partition to consumer must be rebalanced\nand producers must be informed\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
