    },
    {
      "id": "CwvmfBI1s-CVeapa0IEHx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 225,
      "y": 301.5,
      "width": 383.5797119140625,
      "height": 1375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bQB",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1313829426,
      "version": 759,
      "versionNonce": 1360219438,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782702186036,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Questions:\n\n1. imp features?\nUser uploads a post\nUsers feed is posts from friends\nPost can be liked by friends\nPost might contain media\n\n2. media\nyes\n\n3. scale\n300 m users\n\n4. restriction on friends/ followers\nno\n\n5. order of feed?\nchronological\n\nFunctional req:\nUser can upload a post\nPost might contain media\nUsers feed is posts from friends\nPost can be liked by friends ( optional)\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.99\nScalability\nlow latency : 1 second on feed\nReliable\n\nBack of the envelop calc:\n\nStorage:\ntext\n300m users * 1000 post * 1kb\n= 3 * 10^8 * 10^3 kb\n= 300 TB of text storage\n\nmedia \n50% of post have media\n1mb\n300m users * 500 post * 1mb\n= 3 * 10^8 * 5 * 10^2 * 1mb\n= 15 * 10^10 mb\n= 150 pb of media storage\n\nTrafic:\n300 m users\n100 m DAU\n10 times a day\n= 100m * 10 / 10^5\n= 10^3 * 10^6 / 10^5\n= 10000 rps",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Questions:\n\n1. imp features?\nUser uploads a post\nUsers feed is posts from friends\nPost can be liked by friends\nPost might contain media\n\n2. media\nyes\n\n3. scale\n300 m users\n\n4. restriction on friends/ followers\nno\n\n5. order of feed?\nchronological\n\nFunctional req:\nUser can upload a post\nPost might contain media\nUsers feed is posts from friends\nPost can be liked by friends ( optional)\n\nNFR:\nAvailability : 99.99\nScalability\nlow latency : 1 second on feed\nReliable\n\nBack of the envelop calc:\n\nStorage:\ntext\n300m users * 1000 post * 1kb\n= 3 * 10^8 * 10^3 kb\n= 300 TB of text storage\n\nmedia \n50% of post have media\n1mb\n300m users * 500 post * 1mb\n= 3 * 10^8 * 5 * 10^2 * 1mb\n= 15 * 10^10 mb\n= 150 pb of media storage\n\nTrafic:\n300 m users\n100 m DAU\n10 times a day\n= 100m * 10 / 10^5\n= 10^3 * 10^6 / 10^5\n= 10000 rps",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
