    },
    {
      "id": "brZ4fQPCCo2pHPshrwTYt",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 782.0300598144531,
      "y": 1464.1135559082031,
      "width": 526.6595458984375,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bR8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1880464242,
      "version": 265,
      "versionNonce": 1510658542,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782714638833,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Options on fanout\n1. get data during read\nworks for celebrities\n\n2. consolidate during write\ngood for most users\n\nWe take a hybrid approach\nfanout and prepare data during write\nand in real time get posts from celebrities and append",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Options on fanout\n1. get data during read\nworks for celebrities\n\n2. consolidate during write\ngood for most users\n\nWe take a hybrid approach\nfanout and prepare data during write\nand in real time get posts from celebrities and append",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5gNJvNbiKYw0gfaOcOuF1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1589.0300598144531,
      "y": 1099.1135559082031,
      "width": 589.319580078125,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bR9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1144351666,
      "version": 367,
      "versionNonce": 1350415602,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782714780365,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "If replication is by key ranges\nuserId for celebrity will craete a write skew\nhence, we should divide user_id into 10 user_id by appending\nid_1, id_2 ...\nso data can be distributed evenly\n\nif hash partition is use, same problem.\nso divide teh key at app side\n\nor we can add partition key by user_id + ost_id\nbut then we can query get all posts by userId efficiently",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If replication is by key ranges\nuserId for celebrity will craete a write skew\nhence, we should divide user_id into 10 user_id by appending\nid_1, id_2 ...\nso data can be distributed evenly\n\nif hash partition is use, same problem.\nso divide teh key at app side\n\nor we can add partition key by user_id + ost_id\nbut then we can query get all posts by userId efficiently",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yteWJjheDGsp4oVatEfxc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2309.2739669992197,
      "y": 348.60028215550983,
      "width": 624.1754150390625,
      "height": 560,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bRA",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1338047278,
      "version": 224,
      "versionNonce": 702315186,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782715274024,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ranking Pipeline\nModern feeds are not chronlological\n\nthey are based on ML models\n\nCandidates\n↓\nML Ranking\n↓\nBusiness Rules\n↓\nReturn\n\nWe do this in parallel to fanout. ex :\n2000 posts, we select top 50 to display\n\nbased on various factors liek\n\n---\n\nRanking features\nUser features\nCreator features\nPost features\nInteraction features\n\nReal systems use deep learning models with hundreds or thousands of features.\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Ranking Pipeline\nModern feeds are not chronlological\n\nthey are based on ML models\n\nCandidates\n↓\nML Ranking\n↓\nBusiness Rules\n↓\nReturn\n\nWe do this in parallel to fanout. ex :\n2000 posts, we select top 50 to display\n\nbased on various factors liek\n\n---\n\nRanking features\nUser features\nCreator features\nPost features\nInteraction features\n\nReal systems use deep learning models with hundreds or thousands of features.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
